{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.005.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Construction du temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-38: cf. 1 Ch 28:10-12, 20. 2 Ch 3. Ac 7:47.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Ce fut la quatre cent quatre-vingti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e apr\u00e8s la sortie des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte que Salomon b\u00e2tit la maison \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, la quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de son r\u00e8gne sur Isra\u00ebl, au mois de Ziv, qui est le second mois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2","name":"1 Rois 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18","name":"1 Rois 5:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.5.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>La maison que le roi Salomon b\u00e2tit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait soixante coud\u00e9es de longueur, vingt de largeur, et trente de hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3","name":"1 Rois 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1","name":"1 Rois 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le portique devant le temple de la maison avait vingt coud\u00e9es de longueur r\u00e9pondant \u00e0 la largeur de la maison, et dix coud\u00e9es de profondeur sur la face de la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4","name":"1 Rois 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2","name":"1 Rois 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi fit \u00e0 la maison des fen\u00eatres solidement grill\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5","name":"1 Rois 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3","name":"1 Rois 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il b\u00e2tit contre le mur de la maison des \u00e9tages circulaires, qui entouraient les murs de la maison, le temple et le sanctuaire; et il fit des chambres lat\u00e9rales tout autour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6","name":"1 Rois 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4","name":"1 Rois 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>L\u2019\u00e9tage inf\u00e9rieur \u00e9tait large de cinq coud\u00e9es, celui du milieu de six coud\u00e9es, et le troisi\u00e8me de sept coud\u00e9es; car il m\u00e9nagea des retraites \u00e0 la maison tout autour en dehors, afin que la charpente n\u2019entr\u00e2t pas dans les murs de la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7","name":"1 Rois 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5","name":"1 Rois 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019on b\u00e2tit la maison, on se servit de pierres toutes taill\u00e9es, et ni marteau, ni hache, ni aucun instrument de fer, ne furent entendus dans la maison pendant qu\u2019on la construisait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8","name":"1 Rois 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6","name":"1 Rois 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>L\u2019entr\u00e9e des chambres de l\u2019\u00e9tage inf\u00e9rieur \u00e9tait au c\u00f4t\u00e9 droit de la maison; on montait \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tage du milieu par un escalier tournant, et de l\u2019\u00e9tage du milieu au troisi\u00e8me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9","name":"1 Rois 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7","name":"1 Rois 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir achev\u00e9 de b\u00e2tir la maison, Salomon la couvrit de planches et de poutres de c\u00e8dre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10","name":"1 Rois 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8","name":"1 Rois 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Il donna cinq coud\u00e9es de hauteur \u00e0 chacun des \u00e9tages qui entouraient toute la maison, et il les lia \u00e0 la maison par des bois de c\u00e8dre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11","name":"1 Rois 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9","name":"1 Rois 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel adressa la parole \u00e0 Salomon, et lui dit: Tu b\u00e2tis cette maison!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12","name":"1 Rois 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10","name":"1 Rois 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Si tu marches selon mes lois, si tu pratiques mes ordonnances, si tu observes et suis tous mes commandements, j\u2019accomplirai \u00e0 ton \u00e9gard la promesse que j\u2019ai faite \u00e0 David, ton p\u00e8re,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13","name":"1 Rois 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11","name":"1 Rois 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>j\u2019habiterai au milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et je n\u2019abandonnerai point mon peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14","name":"1 Rois 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12","name":"1 Rois 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir achev\u00e9 de b\u00e2tir la maison,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15","name":"1 Rois 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13","name":"1 Rois 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Salomon en rev\u00eatit int\u00e9rieurement les murs de planches de c\u00e8dre, depuis le sol jusqu\u2019au plafond; il rev\u00eatit ainsi de bois l\u2019int\u00e9rieur, et il couvrit le sol de la maison de planches de cypr\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16","name":"1 Rois 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14","name":"1 Rois 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il rev\u00eatit de planches de c\u00e8dre les vingt coud\u00e9es du fond de la maison, depuis le sol jusqu\u2019au haut des murs, et il r\u00e9serva cet espace pour en faire le sanctuaire, le lieu tr\u00e8s saint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17","name":"1 Rois 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15","name":"1 Rois 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Les quarante coud\u00e9es sur le devant formaient la maison, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire le temple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18","name":"1 Rois 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16","name":"1 Rois 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le bois de c\u00e8dre \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la maison offrait des sculptures de coloquintes et de fleurs \u00e9panouies; tout \u00e9tait de c\u00e8dre, on ne voyait aucune pierre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19","name":"1 Rois 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17","name":"1 Rois 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Salomon \u00e9tablit le sanctuaire int\u00e9rieurement au milieu de la maison, pour y placer l\u2019arche de l\u2019alliance de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20","name":"1 Rois 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18","name":"1 Rois 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Le sanctuaire avait vingt coud\u00e9es de longueur, vingt coud\u00e9es de largeur, et vingt coud\u00e9es de hauteur. Salomon le couvrit d\u2019or pur. Il fit devant le sanctuaire un autel de bois de c\u00e8dre et le couvrit d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21","name":"1 Rois 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19","name":"1 Rois 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il couvrit d\u2019or pur l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la maison, et il fit passer le voile dans des cha\u00eenettes d\u2019or devant le sanctuaire, qu\u2019il couvrit d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22","name":"1 Rois 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20","name":"1 Rois 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Il couvrit d\u2019or toute la maison, la maison tout enti\u00e8re, et il couvrit d\u2019or tout l\u2019autel qui \u00e9tait devant le sanctuaire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23","name":"1 Rois 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21","name":"1 Rois 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Il fit dans le sanctuaire deux ch\u00e9rubins de bois d\u2019olivier sauvage, ayant dix coud\u00e9es de hauteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24","name":"1 Rois 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22","name":"1 Rois 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Chacune des deux ailes de l\u2019un des ch\u00e9rubins avait cinq coud\u00e9es, ce qui faisait dix coud\u00e9es de l\u2019extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 d\u2019une de ses ailes \u00e0 l\u2019extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 de l\u2019autre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25","name":"1 Rois 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23","name":"1 Rois 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Le second ch\u00e9rubin avait aussi dix coud\u00e9es. La mesure et la forme \u00e9taient les m\u00eames pour les deux ch\u00e9rubins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26","name":"1 Rois 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24","name":"1 Rois 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>La hauteur de chacun des deux ch\u00e9rubins \u00e9tait de dix coud\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27","name":"1 Rois 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25","name":"1 Rois 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Salomon pla\u00e7a les ch\u00e9rubins au milieu de la maison, dans l\u2019int\u00e9rieur. Leurs ailes \u00e9taient d\u00e9ploy\u00e9es: l\u2019aile du premier touchait \u00e0 l\u2019un des murs, et l\u2019aile du second touchait \u00e0 l\u2019autre mur; et leurs autres ailes se rencontraient par l\u2019extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 au milieu de la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28","name":"1 Rois 6:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26","name":"1 Rois 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Salomon couvrit d\u2019or les ch\u00e9rubins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29","name":"1 Rois 6:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27","name":"1 Rois 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Il fit sculpter sur tout le pourtour des murs de la maison, \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur et \u00e0 l\u2019ext\u00e9rieur, des ch\u00e9rubins, des palmes et des fleurs \u00e9panouies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30","name":"1 Rois 6:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28","name":"1 Rois 6:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Il couvrit d\u2019or le sol de la maison, \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur et \u00e0 l\u2019ext\u00e9rieur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31","name":"1 Rois 6:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29","name":"1 Rois 6:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Il fit \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e du sanctuaire une porte \u00e0 deux battants, de bois d\u2019olivier sauvage; l\u2019encadrement avec les poteaux \u00e9quivalait \u00e0 un cinqui\u00e8me du mur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32","name":"1 Rois 6:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30","name":"1 Rois 6:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Les deux battants \u00e9taient de bois d\u2019olivier sauvage. Il y fit sculpter des ch\u00e9rubins, des palmes et des fleurs \u00e9panouies, et il les couvrit d\u2019or; il \u00e9tendit aussi l\u2019or sur les ch\u00e9rubins et sur les palmes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33","name":"1 Rois 6:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31","name":"1 Rois 6:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Il fit de m\u00eame, pour la porte du temple, des poteaux de bois d\u2019olivier sauvage, ayant le quart de la dimension du mur, et deux battants de bois de cypr\u00e8s;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34","name":"1 Rois 6:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32","name":"1 Rois 6:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>chacun des battants \u00e9tait form\u00e9 de deux planches bris\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35","name":"1 Rois 6:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33","name":"1 Rois 6:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:35","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Il y fit sculpter des ch\u00e9rubins, des palmes et des fleurs \u00e9panouies, et il les couvrit d\u2019or, qu\u2019il \u00e9tendit sur la sculpture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36","name":"1 Rois 6:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34","name":"1 Rois 6:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:36","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Il b\u00e2tit le parvis int\u00e9rieur de trois rang\u00e9es de pierres de taille et d\u2019une rang\u00e9e de poutres de c\u00e8dre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37","name":"1 Rois 6:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35","name":"1 Rois 6:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:37","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>La quatri\u00e8me ann\u00e9e, au mois de Ziv, les fondements de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel furent pos\u00e9s;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38","name":"1 Rois 6:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36","name":"1 Rois 6:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.38","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 6:38","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.006.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.007.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.6.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>et la onzi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e, au mois de Bul, qui est le huiti\u00e8me mois, la maison fut achev\u00e9e dans toutes ses parties et telle qu\u2019elle devait \u00eatre. Salomon la construisit dans l\u2019espace de sept ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6","name":"1 Rois 6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1","name":"1 Rois 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.7.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37","name":"1 Rois 6:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.6.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbb7a55d4.67413047');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb7a55d4.67413047\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbb7a55d4.67413047","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbb7a55d4.67413047'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb7a55d4.67413047\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}